      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3409761252784218388, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteText
      value: 'Day 23


        When I was a kid, I used to stay awake late at night
        listening to the radio.


        I didn''t care what was playing.


        I
        just liked hearing voices.


        It made the darkness feel smaller.


        It''s
        strange.


        I''ve spent most of my life surrounded by people, yet
        I''ve rarely felt less alone than I did during those nights.


        Maybe
        loneliness has nothing to do with being by yourself.


        Maybe it''s
        about feeling unseen.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    m_RemovedComponents: []
