      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2189277595281392803, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_LocalEulerAnglesHint.y
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2189277595281392803, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_LocalEulerAnglesHint.z
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3409761252784218388, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteText
      value: 'Day 7


        I never understood people who claimed they had found
        peace.


        I always thought they were lying.


        Now I''m not
        so sure.


        Maybe peace isn''t feeling happy.


        Maybe it''s
        just not fighting yourself for a few moments.


        If that''s true,
        I think I found it today.


        For about ten seconds.


        A new
        personal record.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
