      propertyPath: m_LocalEulerAnglesHint.y
      value: -54.568
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2189277595281392803, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_LocalEulerAnglesHint.z
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3409761252784218388, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteText
      value: 'Day 31


        Last night I dreamed that something was watching me.


        Not
        with hatred.


        Not with kindness.


        Just watching.


        As
        if it was waiting for me to understand something.


        When I woke up,
        I realized it wasn''t the thing itself that scared me.


        What scared
        me was the feeling that I had nowhere left to hide.


        No excuses.


        No
        lies.


        No substances.


        No masks.


        Just me.


        And
        after all this time, I still don''t know who that is.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
