    - target: {fileID: 3409761252784218388, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteText
      value: 'Day 19


        Some thoughts never really leave.


        People
        think they''re born from despair, but that''s not always true.


        Sometimes
        they come when everything is quiet.


        When the world finally stops
        making noise.


        When you''re left alone with the things you''ve done.


        I
        don''t want to die.


        At least, I don''t think I do.


        But
        I still don''t know how to live with some of my memories.


        Maybe
        that''s what I''m supposed to learn here.


        Not how to survive.


        How
        to live.


        There''s a difference.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
