      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3409761252784218388, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteText
      value: 'Day 12


        Sometimes I try to remember when it all started.


        Not
        the drugs. That''s easy.


        I try to remember when I started believing
        I needed to escape from myself.


        The drugs were just an answer.
        A terrible answer, but an answer nonetheless.


        For years I thought
        the problem was the pain.


        Now I think the problem was the silence
        that came after it.


        When there was nothing left to blame.


        When
        the only person left in the room was me.


        And I didn''t like who
        I was.


        Maybe that''s why I''m still here.


        Because for
        the first time, I can''t hide.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    m_RemovedComponents: []
    m_RemovedGameObjects: []
    m_AddedGameObjects: []
    m_AddedComponents: []
  m_SourcePrefab: {fileID: 100100000, guid: 52fecac8dbd5d4f47aaf33d437ec5c01, type: 3}
